title: HOLLYWOOD PALACE -- Louis Armstrong ( host ), Jimmy Durante
description:
This early 1964 show hosted by Louis Armstrong is also a celebration 
of his 50th anniversary in show business. In addition to Jimmy Durante,
the other famous guests are Dan Rowan & Dick Martin, Diahann Carroll, 
and a poetry reading by actor Edward G. Robinson.

Armstrong came back to perform in several shows over the next 4 years, 
but unlike Durante this is the only Hollywood Palace that he also hosted.
